 => %ODT2BRAILLE_HOME%/ext/liblouis/tables


Build instructions
******************

Linux
=====

 - in the project's root directory, run:
  * ./autogen.sh
  * ./configure
  * make
  * sudo make install


Windows (CodeBlocks)
====================

 - ./configure (on Linux)
 - create a new dynamic linked library project: liblouis
 - delete main.c & main.h
 - add files:
  * %ODT2BRAILLE_HOME%/ext/liblouis/src/release_2.3/liblouis
 - build
 - copy to %ODT2BRAILLE_HOME%/ext/liblouis/bin:
  * liblouis.dll
  * liblouis.a
  * liblouis.def 


Mac OS
======

 - in project's root directory, run:
  * ./autogen.sh
  * ./configure
  * make
  * sudo make install
 - copy to %ODT2BRAILLE_HOME%/ext/liblouis/bin:
  * /usr/local/lib/liblouis.2.dylib


